    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six powertrain. The naturally aspirated 3.2L engine features individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically flawless, this vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis retains its factory-spec damping and handling characteristics, aided by a functional M-Variable differential lock. Finished in concours-ready condition with an immaculate undercarriage and original paint depth, this is a collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
